OL,3,CTraders brand roadworks 'a nightmare'
OL,4,Cas trade hit
OL,6,FBusinesses along the A303 in Somerset
OL,7,Fsay roadworks have been a "nightmare"
OL,8,Fand have badly affected their trade.
OL,10,FThe #155m project is turning a busy
OL,11,Fstretch of the road between Sparkford
OL,12,Fand Ilchester into a dual carriageway,
OL,13,Fbut has suffered delays. It was
OL,14,Foriginally due to be finished this
OL,15,FSpring, but it may now be 2025 before
OL,16,Fthe works are finished.
OL,18,FThose behind the scheme say work is
OL,19,Fpredicted to be completed by Winter
OL,20,F2024-2025.
