OL,3,CTraders brand roadworks 'a nightmare'
OL,4,Cas trade hit
OL,6,FBut business owners operating along
OL,7,Fthe busy route have told ITV News West
OL,8,FCountry that they have been badly
OL,9,Fimpacted by the works.
OL,11,FJoy Whittington has owned The Bakery
OL,12,Fby the A303 since 1989 and is having
OL,13,Fto adapt the business.
OL,15,FShe said: "It's had a financial
OL,16,Fimpact. The last three years, it's
OL,17,Fbeen gradually going down and down and
OL,18,Fdown. A lot of people, they they look
OL,19,Fon the internet they see roadblocks on
OL,20,Fthe A303 in this area. So they travel
OL,21,Fon the A30."
