OL,3,CTraders brand roadworks 'a nightmare'
OL,4,Cas trade hit
OL,6,FThe new A303 has now moved meaning the
OL,7,Ftraffic no longer passes right outside
OL,8,Fthe bakery's shop.
OL,10,FJoy added: "It's terrible. I tried to
OL,11,Fput it out of my mind and think
OL,12,Fpositive all the time. But it never
OL,13,Fgoes away."
OL,15,FSince posting about the issues they
OL,16,Fhave been experiencing on social
OL,17,Fmedia, Joy says she has had an amazing
OL,18,Fresponse from the local community,
OL,19,Fwhich have been supporting the
OL,20,Fbusiness.
