OL,6,FFurther along the A303, the owner of
OL,7,FMattia Diner - a 1950s-style American
OL,8,Fdiner - says the roadworks have also
OL,9,Faffected footfall.
OL,11,FAndrea Mattia said: "Mainly because
OL,12,Fpeople are getting the wrong
OL,13,Finformation, saying the A303 is
OL,14,Fclosed. I mean, I had regular
OL,15,Fcustomers come in the other day and
OL,16,Fthey went the other way to go down to
OL,17,FCornwall and they thought we were
OL,18,Fclosed. It was open."
