OL,6,FAndrea says the electricity supply has
OL,7,Fhad to be cut twice - and signs she
OL,8,Fput up, taken down. But she says it's
OL,9,Fthe unpredictability that has been the
OL,10,Fbiggest issue.
OL,12,F"It's a nightmare because you don't
OL,13,Fknow what's going to happen from this
OL,14,Fday, from one week to another, because
OL,15,Fthere's no warning what we're doing."
