OL,6,FA spokesperson for National Highways
OL,7,Fsaid: "We appreciate that any works,
OL,8,Fparticularly on such a major project
OL,9,Fas the A303 dualling scheme, can
OL,10,Fimpact local communities but we're
OL,11,Fcommitted to minimising any disruption
OL,12,Fand being good neighbours to local
OL,13,Fresidents and businesses during
OL,14,Flifespan of the scheme.
