OL,6,F"Throughout the construction phase, we
OL,7,Fhave engaged extensively with Mattia
OL,8,FDiner and the Bakery, and any other
OL,9,Fbusinesses, landowner or communities
OL,10,Fto address any concerns and will
OL,11,Fcontinue to try our very best to
OL,12,Fminimise any impacts. We always aim to
OL,13,Fmaintain access to businesses,
OL,14,Fallowing them to keep open and
OL,15,Fcontinue trading.
