OL,6,F"The A303 Sparkford to Ilchester
OL,7,Fscheme will deliver desperately needed
OL,8,Fimprovements to tackle the long-
OL,9,Fstanding congestion and safety issues,
OL,10,Fwhile also helping to unlock the
OL,11,Fregional economy.
OL,13,F"We are grateful for people's patience
OL,14,Fwhile we carry out this work and aim
OL,15,Fto complete the scheme as quickly as
OL,16,Fpossible."
